for the night.

16:25.860 --> 16:26.903
Ah!

16:26.945 --> 16:28.988
- Turtle, turtle...
[fizzles out]

16:29.030 --> 16:31.199
- Pfft.
I can do that.

16:31.241 --> 16:33.034
Let's go find
a place to crash.

16:33.076 --> 16:35.161
