- Huh?

16:54.014 --> 16:55.640
Solid recliner, huh?

16:55.682 --> 16:56.766
A lotta leg room.

16:56.808 --> 16:58.393
We could definitely
sleep here, right?

17:04.482 --> 17:05.275
