ten years in a row.

25:36.536 --> 25:38.621
She was a goddamn legend.

25:38.663 --> 25:42.000
[cheering]

25:42.042 --> 25:45.754
We wouldn't be here
without her,

25:45.795 --> 25:49.132
and we--
we will miss her.

25:49.174 --> 25:50.633
Phew.

